data.description: Located on 2 private acres in one of Keene's finest neighborhoods you will find this extraordinary post & beam contemporary. Soaring cathedral ceilings and plenty of natural light with an open-concept floor plan, provide a relaxing environment perfect for entertaining or simply appreciating the quiet sounds of nature. Off the comfortably-sized kitchen and living area is an enclosed sunroom which will surely become your favorite spot in the home. Connected to the sunroom with its southern exposure is the deck which provides some spectacular sunrises and sunsets. Also located on the first floor is a study with a half bath that overlooks the lush greenery in the spring and summer. The upstairs offers three bedrooms, all with lovely natural light, a full bath with a laundry chute and a large storage area. The finished lower-level suite is ideal for multigenerational living with a bedroom, private bath and family room. This property is less than two miles to a vibrant,  quintessential New England downtown with shops, restaurants and a newly updated theatre. It is approximately 2 hours to the White Mountains, NH Seacoast, and the Boston area. This just may be the home you've been looking for!
